texts.text: >The storeroom door opens after removing its rather sturdy lock.
>Inside the dusty room, one man waited for visitors to approach.
>In the corners, weakened Vouivre were huddled together in fear.
Everyone...!
Just when I lost contact with the others, the one that got away comes crawling back.
I didn't think you'd have the Liberators with you though.
I'm guessing the rest are done for.
You know about the Liberators?
Duh. I used to be an Acolyte. You're my worst enemy.
You're the last one.
Give back our garnets and get the hell out of here!
If you don't, I'll get everyone else to attack you at once!
What? You...

*Laugh*
Hey, she took your phone!
Hilarious! You can enslave her by taking her gem,
but instead she takes your phone and makes you do her bidding.
Enslave her? I don't understand.
Wait. You didn't even know that?
Now I get it... And you were just innocently playing along.
These gems are worth an absolute fortune.
Apparently these grant your wish or something too. But there's more.
Taking their gems lets you enslave them.
We had no idea.
That's probably not something she ever would've told us.
I mean this world's full of bad guys like you and me.
Regardless. Wouldn't anyone steal these gems if they had this knowledge?
They'd kill you in a fight, but if you can enslave them it's a moot point.
They're worth a fortune on their own too. Gotta get as many as you can.
A Vouivre that has its garnet taken away is weakened and will eventually die.
Did you know that?
Oh? I knew... But what about it?
I just want the gems and not these snake bitches.
If they curl up and die too then that's just two birds with one stone.
If they got their gems back, I'd be in for a world of hurt too so...
You... Piece of shit!!
>Vouivre flies towards the Dx2 in a fit of rage!
>The Dx2 throws something right in front of Vouivre.
*Scream*
Ugh, that flash...
It's too bright... I can't see...
>Everyone's vision slowly begins to recover...
...! Vouivre!
What a dumbass.
This must be your first time seeing this, yeah?
We used this during the initial raid.
No...
He took it while she was blinded.
I guess he was goading her into it attacking.
Give me that phone.
Here...
>Vouivre hands Jeng Yun's phone to the Dx2.
Don't move. Or I'll have her attack you.
But if you end up killing her, that works too,
so I guess do whatever you want.
This is the worst piece of crap we've seen in a while... I want to kick his ass!
Hahaha! Too bad!
If you took her garnet and made her your slave,
things might've turned out differently.
That's it...
Jeng Yun?
We'll back you up...
I'm going in. Please back me up if he summons any demons.
We can't really stop you so...
Beat the crap out of him, Jeng Yun!
Honey hates him more than pigs that haven't been slaughtered yet!
You both look really pissed.
I guess this is what happens when you poke a sleeping dog...
It'd be a miracle if he somehow lived.
>Jeng Yun takes a step forward.
What...? You serious?
Your phone's over here.
There's no way a human can fight a demon head-on!
Quit while you're ahead!
No!
You moron!
Everyone support Jeng Yun! Don't let anything near him!
I copy! Devil Download!
>The boss summons a demon that immediately goes after Jeng Yun.
>The Liberators' demons block it!
I'll break your phone if you come any closer!
Then do it.
What...?!
Your greed and selfish desire to rob these demons and enslave them...
The way you've treated the Vouivre
cannot be overlooked considering you're a Dx2.
Even if it means I'll lose my Dx2 abilities,
I won't rest until you eat my fist.
What...? I don't understand. You must be crazy.
He already took my garnet,
so there's no reason for you to fight like this...!
Dammit! What the hell are you?!
Vouivre! Attack these assholes! Full power!
>Vouivre puts herself between Jeng Yun and the Dx2!
Stop...
No.
I can't disobey him.
So please. Stop...!
You bitch! I said kill!
*Sob*
>Vouivre aims for Jeng Yun's neck with her sharp claws.
*Wince*
What the hell? How can you guard against that?!
You have to obey the one holding the garnet. I said full power...!
Exactly. I can't hold back out of my own free will...
I'm doing everything I can... Why...?!
Ha!
>Jeng Yun pushes Vouivre to the ground,
>and quickly gets the Dx2 into a chokehold.
S-Stop... I can't... Breathe...!!
*Groan*
>The man's body goes limp.
*Sigh*
Is he dead...?
No. It was a bit rough, but he'll be out for a bit.
Now... I believe this garnet is yours.
*Gasp*
You have to do as the holder says, correct?
(Oh... I guess he's just taking it for himself.)
(It's no different from before.)
(They wanted to take advantage of us this whole time...)
That won't do. It's so important to you.
Please place this back on your forehead.
Huh?
Is something wrong...?
You're giving it back? Why...?
What do you mean, why? It belongs to you.
We still need to return to the other garnets too.
The other Vouivre might not last much longer.
Uh, yeah...
>A few hours later...
Finally! My garnet!
Did it get scratched?
Nope, it's fine!
How do I look? Is it on straight?
I think everyone has their garnet back now.
*Sigh*
The Vouivre look a lot better now!
I'm glad we made it! Such a relief.
Um... Jeng Yun? This is yours.
Oh, my phone. Thank you!
Why are you thanking me...? I stole it from you remember?
Oh, that's right. I already forgot!

*Blush*
You're such an...
I have one more thing to say...
Yes?
I always thought that humans were just greedy garnet thieves,
and pathetic in general... But you're different.
I can't believe in every person,
but I think I can believe in you.
I'm happy to hear that! Thank you!
Y-yeah... So... Umm...

*Squeal*
Just a bit more. You can do it!
I'm getting all worked up just watching...
What is this? I'm going if you don't mind.
Ugh! Will everyone just shut up!
I want to help you and be there for you...
Oh! Then will you join me as an ally?
As equals.
Equals. Ally...
If we're equals, is it okay if I say I don't want to do something?
Is that okay with you?
Yes, of course. I wouldn't have it any other way!
*Blush*
Okay then. Jeng Yun, I'll be your new ally.
I've got a good feeling about us!
